v2.1 - patches for update

Bug Fixes:
+ Fixed Twitchium spawning when I'm not live/not spawning when I am live. [X]
+ Offline Earning now works.
+ Enchanter no longer flashes an expensive price before adjusting to the correct price for skipping. 
+ Auto-buying a crate will continue, even if you cannot afford it after rejoining.
+ Forbidden Gate now correctly shows how many crystals you need to purchase. [X]
+ Updated Corium's description to reflect new behavior. [X]w

Balance Changes:
+ Reduced price of Ocean Crate to 10Oc, from 1N. [X]
- Decreased chance of unboxing Military Dropper to 1/150M, from 1/50M. [X]
- Decreased chance of unboxing Twitchium Dropper to 1/183M, from 1/83M. [X]
- Applying Frost effect to an ore with Fire effect will destroy the ore. [X]
- Applying Fire effect to an ore with Frost effect will destroy the ore. [X]

Changes:
+ Traveling Merchant is now unique per player. [X]

Changes:
+ Added a tooltip for the current potion you are upgrading to in the brewery.
+ If you are on a leaderboard, your name will be highlighted.
+ Potions now pause when the luck is being overriden.
+ New base indicator that tells you whose base is whose, and a teleport back to your base button.
+ For new players, earn a free Legendary for turning on notifications.
+ Odds for items in crates now adjust based on your current luck.
+ Potion crafting now increments by '5', as opposed to one.
+ Added a countdown to the premium shop for Limited items.
+ Revamped settings, see your global stats
+ Secrets show up in middle of screen when unboxxed.
+ Droppers with neon ore now have a description indicating so.

+ Enchant Skipping now scales off of previous prices. See prices below.
common: 100 crystals
uncommon: 500 crystals
rare: 10K crystals
epic: 100k crystals
legendary: 500k crystals
secret: 2.5M crystals

Leaderboard rewards:
+ Daily, weekly rewards
+ Seasons for rewards

Crate UI:
+ Show how many of a given crate you've unboxxed.

ROADMAP:
Cutscenes:
+ Cutscene for new players, to show a high level overview of how the game works.
+ Cutscene on join, if a player has offline earnings.
+ Cutscene for unboxxing a Secret item


Gifting rewards:
+ Give players items for gifting to other players.
+ Tiers for players that have gifted more, later tiers are mostly decorations.

Better Onboarding/Tutorial:
+ Should give players goals until 2nd-3rd rebirth.
+ Nudge players to explore the map, find Periastron Crate.
+ Nudge players to find travelling merchant.

Daily Gifts:
+ Every day, claim a gift that awards crystals, potions, and an item, based on how much money you have.

Potion Menu:
+ NEW SETTING: Auto consume potions, no matter what.
+ Option to consume many potions at once.
+ Pop-up to say "are you sure you want to use X potions for X time?"

New Build Mode:
+ Axis Binding, while clicking and dragging to place, items will stay bound to the same line. -- note to self, no gaps
+ Box Select, to quickly select bulk items!
+ Brand new build mode, a menu instead of sidebar.
+ Adjustable keybinds (see settings)
+ All keybinds visible on screen, whenever relevant
+ Placing an upgrader on top of another upgrader, if the conveyors align, and are the same direciton, will replace the upgrader/conveyor. -- reach goal
+ Hide other bases setting (hide everybody else's base)
+ Withdraw all button
+ Remove mode, click on an item to remove it!
+ Shiny/Mythic items have an indictor in inventory.
+ Miner's Haven keybinds option.
+ Miner's Haven build mode, for mobile.
+ Items inside of enchanter are shown in inventory, with a beaker next to them to indicate they are being enchanted.
+ Searching for a crate in inventory shows items in that crate
+ Hover to view an item's name
+ Inspect to view an item's stats/tooltip

Better Building Feedback:
+ Pop ups on base to show where ore is dying, which upgraders are failing, and where ore is getting stuck.

